00:02:35,500 --> 00:02:40,500
Stage 1 begins: Ingesting weather data for the 10 global cities.

34
00:02:40,500 --> 00:02:46,000
The script successfully fetches and saves real-time weather forecasts into raw JSON files.

35
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:51,000
